1
00:01:49,460 --> 00:01:54,940
[A Dream Within A Dream]

2
00:01:55,009 --> 00:01:57,940
[Episode 19]

3
00:01:58,030 --> 00:02:01,950
[Song Residence]

4
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:06,840
Are these the betrothal gifts

5
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:08,080
from Her Ladyship?

6
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,000
Of course not, Madam.

7
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,080
These small gifts

8
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:15,680
are just to help calm Miss Song's nerves.

9
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:17,430
Her Ladyship said

10
00:02:17,430 --> 00:02:19,240
Miss Song is well-educated
and well-mannered.

11
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:21,590
She must have been frightened that day.

12
00:02:21,590 --> 00:02:22,960
She's been thinking about her

13
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,870
and sent me to invite her

14
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:26,870
to stay at the Fanghua Hall
for a few days.

15
00:02:26,870 --> 00:02:27,630
Madam…

16
00:02:27,630 --> 00:02:28,280
What?

17
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:29,840
No way!

18
00:02:30,590 --> 00:02:32,450
She has neither an official title

19
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:34,280
nor an imperial decree.

20
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,960
How can she just go like that?

21
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,560
Absolutely not.

22
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,360
I don't approve.

23
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,360
If Her Ladyship has given the order,

24
00:02:40,150 --> 00:02:41,800
then Yimeng should get ready

25
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:42,960
and go.

26
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:44,680
Master.

27
00:02:45,079 --> 00:02:46,430
If she really goes,

28
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:47,840
doesn't that make her engagement

29
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,400
to His Highness official?

30
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,310
Didn't you oppose it?

31
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:52,680
Who runs this house,
you or me?

32
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,430
I mean…

33
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,820
Go invite Miss Song to the palace.

34
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,190
Yes.

35
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:15,430
I-Is

36
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:16,870
such fanfare

37
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,400
really necessary?

38
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,400
Miss Song,

39
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:22,030
Her Ladyship said

40
00:03:22,079 --> 00:03:23,240
whatever others get,

41
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,280
you should have too.

42
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,360
And what they don't get,

43
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,820
you should still be given.

44
00:03:27,470 --> 00:03:28,280
Please.

45
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:38,300
[How to Not Marry a Prince – Day One]

46
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,079
My Lady,

47
00:03:38,329 --> 00:03:39,010
[Fanghua Hall]

48
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:40,430
Miss Song is here.

49
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:42,470
I'm Song Yimeng.

50
00:03:42,470 --> 00:03:43,310
Greetings, My Lady.

51
00:03:43,310 --> 00:03:43,960
Yimeng,

52
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:44,680
come here.

53
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:47,630
You're

54
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:48,840
such a sweet girl.

55
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:50,630
I really like you.

56
00:03:51,030 --> 00:03:52,690
Thank you for the compliment.

57
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:55,240
In the past, I used to think

58
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:57,590
if any girl liked Heng,

59
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:59,280
no matter if she was pretty or ugly,

60
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,280
no matter her temper,

61
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,030
I would

62
00:04:01,030 --> 00:04:02,800
help him marry her.

63
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,750
But I didn't expect

64
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,280
Heng to have such good taste.

65
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:08,240
He fell for a kind

66
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:10,560
and lovely girl like you.

67
00:04:11,470 --> 00:04:12,470
One day,

68
00:04:12,630 --> 00:04:14,360
if I can no longer hold on,

69
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:16,160
I'll leave him in your hands

70
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,800
without worry.

71
00:04:19,950 --> 00:04:20,750
My Lady,

72
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:25,600
I'm afraid I can't accept that.

73
00:04:28,630 --> 00:04:30,630
I don't have feelings
for the Seventh Prince,

74
00:04:30,630 --> 00:04:32,630
and I never thought of marrying him.

75
00:04:33,830 --> 00:04:35,270
To be honest with you,

76
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,040
I actually came

77
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:39,370
to the palace this time
to ask for your help

78
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,210
in calling off the engagement.

79
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,480
Calling it off?

80
00:04:42,630 --> 00:04:43,360
Why?

81
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:45,270
Do you believe those rumors too

82
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,159
and think Heng brings bad luck?

83
00:04:47,159 --> 00:04:47,950
No, no,

84
00:04:48,130 --> 00:04:50,010
that's not it at all.

85
00:04:50,270 --> 00:04:50,830
I-It's

86
00:04:50,830 --> 00:04:51,830
because…

87
00:04:52,070 --> 00:04:52,600
because…

88
00:04:55,330 --> 00:04:56,120
Even if I told you,

89
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,480
you wouldn't believe it.

90
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,430
Anyway, I can't marry him,

91
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,630
and I won't.

92
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:02,600
Please forgive me, My Lady.

93
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:06,360
Your marriage to Heng is no small matter.

94
00:05:06,630 --> 00:05:09,070
It must be carefully considered.

95
00:05:13,870 --> 00:05:14,510
[Moonlit Blossoms]

96
00:05:14,510 --> 00:05:18,190
[How to Not Marry a Prince – Day Two]

97
00:05:27,050 --> 00:05:29,050
Why haven't you taken a single bite?

98
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:30,240
You don't like them?

99
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:32,470
How could I eat them?

100
00:05:33,830 --> 00:05:36,020
It looks like a feast.

101
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:37,610
And look over there.

102
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:40,480
It's like they're dressing me
for fashion week.

103
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,270
Her Ladyship

104
00:05:41,270 --> 00:05:43,480
is dead set on marrying me to Nan Heng.

105
00:05:43,630 --> 00:05:45,830
If I eat, wear, and use these things,

106
00:05:45,830 --> 00:05:48,560
won't I owe her big time?

107
00:05:51,630 --> 00:05:52,430
No way.

108
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:55,680
I have to find a way to return the favor

109
00:05:55,870 --> 00:05:58,070
and convince Her Ladyship that

110
00:05:58,070 --> 00:06:00,270
I must not marry His Highness.

111
00:06:01,070 --> 00:06:02,950
Her Ladyship is used to

112
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:04,680
all kinds of luxurious things.

113
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,630
How can you return her favor?

114
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,470
I have an idea.

115
00:06:19,830 --> 00:06:20,680
My Lady,

116
00:06:21,070 --> 00:06:22,870
it's time to take your medicine.

117
00:06:31,950 --> 00:06:34,680
My future daughter-in-law
is about to slip away.

118
00:06:34,750 --> 00:06:37,000
What's the point of the regimen?

119
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,480
My Lady,

120
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,800
I heard that

121
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:43,800
Miss Song has been sighing
in her room all the time,

122
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,830
looking upset.

123
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:47,480
If you don't come up with something soon,

124
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,830
this engagement really might

125
00:06:48,830 --> 00:06:50,680
be called off.

126
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:57,480
Tell me.

127
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:01,000
If I pick a few concubines for Heng,

128
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:03,560
do you think Yimeng might change her mind?

129
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,270
My Lady,

130
00:07:04,630 --> 00:07:06,870
are you trying to help

131
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,720
or making things worse?

132
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,270
You don't get it.

133
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,560
As long as

134
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:13,160
Chu Guihong

135
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,220
keeps chasing her,

136
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:16,480
she'll never see how great Heng is.

137
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,630
Once there's competition,

138
00:07:20,630 --> 00:07:21,830
she'll see his worth.

139
00:07:22,070 --> 00:07:23,480
Brilliant move, My Lady!

140
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:29,370
[How to Not Marry a Prince – Day Three]

141
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,480
My Lady.

142
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:31,040
I made

143
00:07:31,070 --> 00:07:33,830
some tea drinks just for you.

144
00:07:34,390 --> 00:07:35,240
Have a taste.

145
00:07:36,690 --> 00:07:38,820
[Bubble Tea]

146
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:38,920
What is this?

147
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,830
My Lady,

148
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:41,390
it's called

149
00:07:41,390 --> 00:07:43,270
bubble tea.

150
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:45,870
You can get it with half sugar,
full sugar, or no sugar—

151
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:47,270
iced, with no ice, or at room temperature.

152
00:07:47,270 --> 00:07:49,240
The base teas are black, green, or oolong.

153
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,830
There are flavors like osmanthus,
rose, and crabapple,

154
00:07:50,830 --> 00:07:53,120
and you can add things
like sweet fermented rice balls.

155
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:55,070
You can try all of them if you'd like.

156
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:56,430
Bubble tea?

157
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:03,070
Not bad.

158
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:05,870
Yimeng,

159
00:08:06,160 --> 00:08:07,430
as it happens,

160
00:08:07,430 --> 00:08:10,240
I actually have something
to discuss with you.

161
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,040
My Lady.

162
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:19,070
My Lady.

163
00:08:19,430 --> 00:08:21,480
Aside from Miss Song Yiting,
who's feeling unwell,

164
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:24,080
all the other madams
and young ladies are here.

165
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,390
That's fine.

166
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,560
Greetings, My Lady.

167
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:31,480
Yimeng just brought some bubble tea.

168
00:08:29,820 --> 00:08:31,730
[Black Tea Pudding,
Jasmine Milk Tea, Misty Milk Tea]

169
00:08:31,830 --> 00:08:33,789
Ladies, please take a seat

170
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:35,240
and enjoy it together.

171
00:08:35,990 --> 00:08:37,270
Thank you, My Lady.

172
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,960
It's sweet and tasty.

173
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:49,670
Look at mine.

174
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:50,840
What does yours say?

175
00:08:51,750 --> 00:08:52,960
Oolong milk tea.

176
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:54,560
What are matcha pearls?

177
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:55,750
It tastes good.

178
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,030
I haven't had it before.

179
00:09:01,030 --> 00:09:01,480
Same here.

180
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:02,480
It's really good.

181
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:11,520
I've invited you all here today

182
00:09:11,630 --> 00:09:13,000
because there's something urgent

183
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,600
I'd like to discuss with you.

184
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:15,750
My Lady,

185
00:09:16,030 --> 00:09:17,630
you flatter us.

186
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,480
If you need anything,

187
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,840
just say the word.

188
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,670
Exactly.

189
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:27,390
Heng is my only son.

190
00:09:27,630 --> 00:09:30,200
He spent years stationed at the border.

191
00:09:30,550 --> 00:09:31,390
Now it's time

192
00:09:31,390 --> 00:09:34,390
for him to get married
and carry on the royal line.

193
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,670
Aside from Yimeng,

194
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,440
your daughters

195
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:40,480
are the most graceful and virtuous

196
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,750
in the capital.

197
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:43,030
All fine matches.

198
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,200
What does this mean?

199
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:48,910
My Lady,

200
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,670
hasn't His Highness already been engaged

201
00:09:50,670 --> 00:09:53,000
to the eldest daughter of the Song family?

202
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,480
According to tradition,

203
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:56,480
a prince may have one principal consort

204
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,670
and up to two concubines.

205
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:01,630
Miss Jia,

206
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,970
are you engaged yet?

207
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,770
Guess she's not lucky enough
to marry the prince.

208
00:10:10,770 --> 00:10:13,700
Her fiancé is just about
to send the betrothal gifts.

209
00:10:14,670 --> 00:10:16,050
But I heard that

210
00:10:16,230 --> 00:10:17,960
you're still shopping around.

211
00:10:18,010 --> 00:10:19,390
You've basically

212
00:10:19,390 --> 00:10:21,360
visited every matchmaker in the capital.

213
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,150
Are you lying

214
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:24,200
to Her Ladyship
because you think His Highness

215
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:25,670
isn't good enough for your daughter?

216
00:10:25,670 --> 00:10:26,630
Mrs. Song,

217
00:10:26,670 --> 00:10:29,070
Miss Yiting is famous
all over the capital.

218
00:10:29,300 --> 00:10:30,840
Why don't you say yes?

219
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,240
My eldest daughter

220
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,240
is the prince's principal consort.

221
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:37,440
If my second daughter
became his concubine,

222
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,100
wouldn't that be ridiculous?

223
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,870
Even if I agreed,

224
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:42,960
surely Her Ladyship wouldn't.

225
00:10:44,790 --> 00:10:46,150
I agree.

226
00:10:46,630 --> 00:10:48,550
What's wrong with two sisters

227
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:49,840
sharing a husband?

228
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,390
Oh right, Mrs. Liu,

229
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,790
I heard that

230
00:10:54,810 --> 00:10:57,390
your daughter's birth chart
is incredibly auspicious,

231
00:10:57,390 --> 00:10:59,000
and she's a perfect match for the prince.

232
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,750
Why don't you seize

233
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:03,010
this once-in-a-lifetime opportunity?

234
00:11:05,390 --> 00:11:06,480
My daughter's…

235
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:09,130
birth chart is indeed good,

236
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,870
b-but…

237
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:14,370
her grandfather just passed away.

238
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,360
She's still in mourning.

239
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,480
But if I recall correctly,

240
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:19,880
your father passed away
over ten years ago.

241
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,670
Why do I feel that

242
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:26,840
none of you want

243
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:29,200
your daughters to marry Heng?

244
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:31,150
Is there something wrong with him?

245
00:11:31,150 --> 00:11:32,030
No.

246
00:11:32,670 --> 00:11:34,150
My Lady, you've misunderstood.

247
00:11:34,150 --> 00:11:36,350
His Highness is brilliant and valiant.

248
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,630
It's not that my daughter

249
00:11:37,630 --> 00:11:39,870
refuses to be his concubine.

250
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:40,790
It's just…

251
00:11:43,550 --> 00:11:44,360
just that…

252
00:11:45,550 --> 00:11:47,240
there's still Song Yimeng.

253
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:47,840
Yeah.

254
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:49,270
I-It's because of Song Yimeng.

255
00:11:49,270 --> 00:11:50,080
Me?

256
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:51,630
Exactly.

257
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:54,200
Everyone in the capital knows that

258
00:11:54,540 --> 00:11:56,480
Miss Song is rude, spoiled,

259
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,680
grumpy, and jealous.

260
00:11:58,030 --> 00:12:01,030
If any other girl had to
share His Highness with you,

261
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:04,230
she'd be tormented to death.

262
00:12:05,130 --> 00:12:05,800
[Misty Milk Tea]

263
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:08,790
Yes!

264
00:12:08,990 --> 00:12:09,780
Song Yimeng

265
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,240
is downright vicious.

266
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,480
She has done more wrongs

267
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:13,600
than you can count.

268
00:12:15,670 --> 00:12:17,150
S-Song Yimeng

269
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,390
bullied people

270
00:12:19,670 --> 00:12:21,400
and terrorized her neighbors.

271
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,000
Song Yimeng

272
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:26,960
kicked down widows' doors,

273
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,180
dug up graves,

274
00:12:28,630 --> 00:12:30,690
and beat up the disabled.

275
00:12:30,870 --> 00:12:31,670
Yes, yes, yes!

276
00:12:31,670 --> 00:12:32,110
Exactly!

277
00:12:32,110 --> 00:12:32,750
Yeah.

278
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:33,480
Yeah.

279
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:34,080
Yeah.

280
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:34,870
Yeah, yeah.

281
00:12:38,460 --> 00:12:40,450
I see what's going on now.

282
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:41,550
So basically,

283
00:12:41,550 --> 00:12:44,430
you're trashing me

284
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:46,860
just to get out of marrying Nan Heng, huh?

285
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:48,790
What trashing?

286
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,030
Heng?

287
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,530
What are you doing here?

288
00:13:09,870 --> 00:13:10,790
The ladies

289
00:13:10,810 --> 00:13:13,540
were just talking about
your marriage to Yimeng.

290
