451
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:09,440
To them,

452
00:21:10,350 --> 00:21:13,000
I'm just the murderous God of Death.

453
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:15,310
Then explain it to those

454
00:21:15,310 --> 00:21:16,790
who misunderstand you.

455
00:21:17,030 --> 00:21:18,160
Tell them the truth.

456
00:21:22,750 --> 00:21:23,800
If I

457
00:21:24,030 --> 00:21:24,880
explained it to you,

458
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:26,080
would you believe me?

459
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:32,120
