explaining myself to anyone else?

465
00:21:55,850 --> 00:21:57,060
Was I…

466
00:21:58,030 --> 00:21:59,720
a little too harsh on you?

467
00:22:04,680 --> 00:22:06,160
Yeah, you were.

468
00:22:09,270 --> 00:22:10,070
But...

469
00:22:12,030 --> 00:22:12,880
