I get what you're saying.

583
00:27:13,110 --> 00:27:13,970
I won't send you

584
00:27:14,510 --> 00:27:17,510
any more paintings.

585
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:28,310
Mr. Li,

586
00:27:28,830 --> 00:27:29,830
I didn't send you

587
00:27:29,960 --> 00:27:31,640
those paintings just to say thank you.

588
00:27:31,640 --> 00:27:32,640
Like you said,

589
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:34,940
I sent you 73 paintings in three days.

590
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:36,830
Who does that

591
00:27:36,830 --> 00:27:38,400
just to say thank you?

592
00:27:39,680 --> 00:27:40,880
I like you.

593
00:27:57,400 --> 00:28:00,110
But you're pretty, talented,

594
00:28:00,750 --> 00:28:02,070
and from a powerful family.

595
00:28:02,070 --> 00:28:03,730
You're like a cloud in the sky.

596
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:05,720
I have nothing to my name

597
00:28:05,720 --> 00:28:07,110
and am always risking my life.

598
00:28:07,110 --> 00:28:08,480
I'm like the mud on the ground.

599
00:28:08,480 --> 00:28:09,880
We are so different.

600
00:28:09,880 --> 00:28:12,160
You're way out of my league.

601
00:28:12,640 --> 00:28:13,500
How about this?

602
00:28:14,790 --> 00:28:16,640
Let's finish this cup of tea

603
00:28:17,030 --> 00:28:19,750
and go our separate ways.

604
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:26,550
I see.

605
00:28:27,240 --> 00:28:28,070
Mr. Li,

606
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:30,110
you're refusing me.

607
00:28:33,270 --> 00:28:36,310
Falling petals want to follow the stream,

608
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:39,880
but the stream has no interest in them.

609
00:28:41,480 --> 00:28:42,790
Love

610
00:28:43,110 --> 00:28:45,070
can't be forced.

611
00:28:47,110 --> 00:28:47,960
I'll drink…

612
00:28:50,110 --> 00:28:51,350
this cup of tea.

613
00:29:01,270 --> 00:29:02,800
Sure, I'm a cloud in the sky,

614
00:29:03,240 --> 00:29:04,750
but since I like you,

615
00:29:05,030 --> 00:29:06,830
you're hardly mud on the ground.

616
00:29:07,310 --> 00:29:08,880
I'm just surprised that

617
00:29:09,350 --> 00:29:12,110
someone as free-spirited as you

618
00:29:12,830 --> 00:29:14,680
would care about family status.

619
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:19,730
You've lived a sheltered life.

620
00:29:20,000 --> 00:29:22,000
How could you know how tough life is?

621
00:29:24,350 --> 00:29:25,880
People in the martial world

622
00:29:26,240 --> 00:29:28,400
don't get a monthly salary,

623
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:30,400
own land, or have houses.

624
00:29:30,480 --> 00:29:31,740
Home is wherever we go.

625
00:29:33,270 --> 00:29:35,270
You won't even drink from a cup here,

626
00:29:35,750 --> 00:29:37,270
but I'm usually out there

627
00:29:37,510 --> 00:29:40,350
surviving on whatever I can find.

628
00:30:02,400 --> 00:30:04,200
I can drink this tea,

629
00:30:05,310 --> 00:30:06,840
but it looks like you can't.

630
00:30:10,030 --> 00:30:11,830
It seems you didn't get my point.

631
00:30:11,830 --> 00:30:12,030
I...

632
00:30:12,030 --> 00:30:12,750
I get it.

633
00:30:12,750 --> 00:30:14,000
You don't get a salary,

634
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:15,550
but I can support you
with my monthly allowance

635
00:30:15,550 --> 00:30:16,640
from my family.

636
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:18,830
Land and houses are no problem.

637
00:30:19,000 --> 00:30:21,260
Across all 36 prefectures of Great Jing,

638
00:30:21,270 --> 00:30:23,480
the Song family has estates everywhere.

639
00:30:23,480 --> 00:30:25,110
If you want to roam the world,

640
00:30:25,480 --> 00:30:26,680
as long as you marry me,

641
00:30:26,680 --> 00:30:28,680
my home will be your home.

642
00:30:28,790 --> 00:30:29,590
No, wait,

643
00:30:29,880 --> 00:30:31,210
how could I accept that?

644
00:30:31,270 --> 00:30:32,960
I'd be living off a woman.

645
00:30:33,270 --> 00:30:34,790
When two people love each other,

646
00:30:34,790 --> 00:30:37,070
nothing else matters.

647
00:30:38,640 --> 00:30:40,070
If you keep me happy,

648
00:30:40,270 --> 00:30:42,350
who cares who pays the bills?

649
00:30:43,510 --> 00:30:45,170
B-But what if I don't like you?

650
00:30:45,510 --> 00:30:46,840
What if I'm not into you?

651
00:30:47,480 --> 00:30:49,270
Then I'll make you fall for me.

652
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:51,660
You just said it yourself,

653
00:30:51,680 --> 00:30:52,880
someone like me

654
00:30:53,270 --> 00:30:54,440
is admired by countless people.

655
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:54,680
But

656
00:30:54,680 --> 00:30:56,550
I'm not one of them.

657
00:30:56,550 --> 00:30:57,350
Look at me.

658
00:30:57,680 --> 00:30:59,030
I love freedom.

659
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:00,960
I don't want to be tied to anyone.

660
00:31:05,270 --> 00:31:06,240
Mr. Li,

661
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:08,270
running a place this big

662
00:31:09,030 --> 00:31:10,720
must give you little freedom.

663
00:31:14,030 --> 00:31:15,560
You hit the nail on the head.

664
00:31:17,070 --> 00:31:17,880
That's right.

665
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:20,770
I need to keep
Waning River Crescent running.

666
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:23,030
Building a career

667
00:31:23,030 --> 00:31:24,510
is my top priority right now.

668
00:31:24,510 --> 00:31:25,350
Romance

669
00:31:25,350 --> 00:31:26,830
just gets in the way of business

670
00:31:26,830 --> 00:31:27,830
and making money.

671
00:31:29,750 --> 00:31:31,200
A month has 30 days.

672
00:31:31,440 --> 00:31:32,640
I spend five playing the qin,

673
00:31:32,640 --> 00:31:33,680
five reading,

674
00:31:33,680 --> 00:31:34,720
five painting,

675
00:31:35,070 --> 00:31:36,640
five out with my friends,

676
00:31:36,750 --> 00:31:38,510
and five with my parents.

677
00:31:39,270 --> 00:31:40,750
The days I need you

678
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:42,270
add up to just five.

679
00:31:42,790 --> 00:31:43,680
On those five days,

680
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:46,480
I'll pay you double your daily take.

681
00:31:46,480 --> 00:31:47,830
You won't lose a cent.

682
00:31:50,830 --> 00:31:52,840
[Three years ago]

683
00:31:51,480 --> 00:31:52,830
I can run it for you.

684
00:31:53,030 --> 00:31:54,580
But let me make it clear.

685
00:31:54,750 --> 00:31:56,150
A month has 30 days.

686
00:31:56,240 --> 00:31:57,590
I spend five traveling,

687
00:31:57,720 --> 00:31:58,880
five playing the flute,

688
00:31:58,880 --> 00:32:00,160
five feasting,

689
00:32:00,160 --> 00:32:01,440
five visiting old friends,

690
00:32:01,440 --> 00:32:02,400
and five…

691
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:05,550
I'm not telling you.

692
00:32:05,750 --> 00:32:06,550
In short,

693
00:32:06,880 --> 00:32:09,000
I can only stay here five days a month

694
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:10,590
to run this place for you.

695
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:11,480
How's that?

696
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:15,960
Wait,

697
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:17,690
is that how you treat feelings?

698
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:19,440
Can money fix everything?

699
00:32:20,200 --> 00:32:21,270
Can your money buy company

700
00:32:21,270 --> 00:32:22,350
or true affection?

701
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:25,070
Money is just a worldly thing.

702
00:32:25,350 --> 00:32:27,880
If money can solve matters of the heart,

703
00:32:28,160 --> 00:32:29,240
why not use it?

704
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:31,590
What I want is you

705
00:32:31,880 --> 00:32:32,740
and your heart.

706
00:32:33,350 --> 00:32:35,720
Love not weighed down by money

707
00:32:36,030 --> 00:32:37,590
is the purest love of all.

708
00:32:42,550 --> 00:32:44,070
L-Let me think.

709
00:32:44,270 --> 00:32:45,270
Let me think.

710
00:32:47,880 --> 00:32:48,640
Mr. Li.

711
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:50,000
Think it over.

712
00:32:51,480 --> 00:32:52,680
I'll wait right here…

713
00:32:54,510 --> 00:32:55,680
for your answer.

714
00:33:02,540 --> 00:33:03,650
[Chuyun Palace]

715
00:33:31,990 --> 00:33:32,780
My Lady,

716
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:34,240
you sent for me?

717
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:34,960
Yimeng,

718
00:33:34,960 --> 00:33:35,790
come here.

719
00:33:36,510 --> 00:33:37,310
My Lady,

720
00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:39,120
are you feeling any better?

721
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:42,640
I made some snacks just for Heng,

722
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:43,640
but he left in a hurry

723
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:44,970
and forgot to take them.

724
00:33:45,550 --> 00:33:46,830
Go catch up to him.

725
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:49,110
Give them to him for me.

726
00:33:50,640 --> 00:33:51,790
Isn't this

727
00:33:51,880 --> 00:33:54,160
something Eunuch Yang should do?

728
00:33:54,790 --> 00:33:56,030
But look around.

729
00:33:56,440 --> 00:33:57,790
In this entire hall,

730
00:33:57,960 --> 00:33:59,440
is there anyone else?

731
00:34:03,880 --> 00:34:04,640
My Lady,

732
00:34:04,960 --> 00:34:08,150
isn't that a little too obvious?

733
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:09,920
Good girl,

734
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:12,070
since you know what I want,

735
00:34:12,070 --> 00:34:13,760
go chase after him now.

736
00:34:15,030 --> 00:34:15,840
But

737
00:34:15,960 --> 00:34:16,760
My Lady,

738
00:34:16,800 --> 00:34:18,280
His Highness and me…

739
00:34:18,480 --> 00:34:20,030
w-we...

740
00:34:22,840 --> 00:34:25,040
Since drinking the milk tea yesterday,

741
00:34:25,360 --> 00:34:28,670
I've been feeling so uncomfortable.

742
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:30,280
Fine, I'll go.

743
00:34:30,320 --> 00:34:31,480
I'll go right now.

744
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:40,840
I heard you made a scene
in the Fanghua Hall yesterday

745
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:43,880
and scared those
noble ladies half to death.

746
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:46,670
Song Yimeng is my principal consort.

747
00:34:46,670 --> 00:34:48,800
How could I let people speak ill of her?

748
00:34:48,840 --> 00:34:50,360
Judging from your tone,

749
00:34:51,190 --> 00:34:52,760
the marriage with the Song family

750
00:34:52,760 --> 00:34:54,400
is already set in stone.

751
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:59,620
Uncle, why does this
matter concern you so much?

752
00:35:00,320 --> 00:35:01,320
Regarding the enfeoffment,

753
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:03,630
it's clear that His Majesty
has revived the old rule

754
00:35:03,630 --> 00:35:05,440
from the previous dynasty
just to target you.

755
00:35:05,440 --> 00:35:08,480
Yet the Eighteenth Prince
runs to the Song Residence every day,

756
00:35:08,480 --> 00:35:09,920
showering Miss Song Yiting

757
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:12,030
with attention and gifts,

758
00:35:12,510 --> 00:35:14,110
showing no restraint at all.

759
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:17,970
I have my own plan for the enfeoffment.

760
00:35:18,590 --> 00:35:19,550
As for Nan Rui,

761
00:35:20,550 --> 00:35:22,320
although I don't know Song Yiting,

762
00:35:22,320 --> 00:35:24,880
I doubt she thinks much of Nan Rui.

763
00:35:25,550 --> 00:35:27,110
Miss Song Yiting may not care,

764
00:35:27,110 --> 00:35:29,840
but her mother, Madam Zhou, clearly does.

765
00:35:31,280 --> 00:35:32,880
My view remains the same:

766
00:35:33,670 --> 00:35:36,000
rather than letting
Miss Song Yiting marry someone else

767
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:37,730
and strengthen another force,

768
00:35:37,840 --> 00:35:40,480
you should marry both Song sisters.

769
00:35:40,970 --> 00:35:42,800
A wife should be chosen for her virtue,

770
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:44,260
a concubine for her looks.

771
00:35:45,070 --> 00:35:48,070
We need to get a firm grip
on the Song family's power.

772
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:51,360
My answer

773
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:53,920
hasn't changed.

774
00:35:55,550 --> 00:35:56,360
Absurd.

775
00:35:56,510 --> 00:35:57,360
Good.

776
00:36:14,110 --> 00:36:16,240
A wife should be chosen for her virtue,

777
00:36:16,670 --> 00:36:18,480
a concubine for her looks?

778
00:36:19,150 --> 00:36:20,110
Good?

779
00:36:25,770 --> 00:36:32,550
[A Dream of Qingning,
Episode 22, Scene 12]

780
00:36:27,030 --> 00:36:27,710
Nan Heng!

781
00:36:37,030 --> 00:36:38,590
Instead of staying at home,

782
00:36:38,800 --> 00:36:40,070
what are you doing here?

783
00:36:40,070 --> 00:36:42,280
If I hadn't followed her here,

784
00:36:43,280 --> 00:36:45,000
I wouldn't have known you two

785
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:46,760
were so shameless!

786
00:36:48,360 --> 00:36:49,280
Song Yiting!

787
00:36:50,130 --> 00:36:52,060
He is your brother-in-law!

788
00:36:54,110 --> 00:36:55,590
He used to be.

789
00:36:56,030 --> 00:36:56,890
But from now on,

790
00:36:57,110 --> 00:36:58,480
he'll be my husband.

791
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:02,130
I'll let you be his principal consort,

792
00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:04,070
but keep this in mind:

793
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:05,670
the one he loves most

794
00:37:06,750 --> 00:37:07,810
is me.

795
00:37:11,480 --> 00:37:12,800
That's not true.

796
00:37:13,070 --> 00:37:14,070
That's not true!

797
00:37:23,590 --> 00:37:24,480
What I choose to do

798
00:37:24,480 --> 00:37:25,810
is none of your concern.

799
00:37:26,400 --> 00:37:27,190
Get out!

800
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:29,670
Oh no.

801
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:32,140
That toxic scene

802
00:37:32,230 --> 00:37:33,030
is coming.

803
00:37:33,780 --> 00:37:35,450
[Iconic Scenes in the Script]

804
00:37:35,530 --> 00:37:38,700
[4. The Sister-in-Law
and the Brother-in-Law's Affair]

805
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:42,240
[Immoral]

806
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:48,480
It's so late,

807
00:37:48,630 --> 00:37:50,830
and Mr. Li still hasn't given an answer.

808
00:37:51,550 --> 00:37:53,400
Guess that's a no.

809
00:37:57,480 --> 00:37:58,280
My Lady,

810
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:00,920
just let it go and look ahead.

811
00:38:01,110 --> 00:38:02,230
The world is vast.

812
00:38:02,280 --> 00:38:04,280
There are millions of good men out there.

813
00:38:04,280 --> 00:38:06,400
You're sure to meet someone better.

814
00:38:09,550 --> 00:38:10,360
Oh no.

815
00:38:10,710 --> 00:38:12,630
You left your handkerchief on the table.

816
00:38:12,630 --> 00:38:14,840
Something that personal must be retrieved.

817
00:38:14,840 --> 00:38:15,630
Please wait here.

818
00:38:15,630 --> 00:38:17,030
I'll go back and fetch it.

819
00:39:46,700 --> 00:39:47,540
Qianyu?

820
00:39:49,660 --> 00:39:50,660
This is...

821
00:39:51,960 --> 00:39:53,620
Qianyu Moon-Cleaving Blade.

822
00:40:07,070 --> 00:40:08,280
As soon as Chief is gone,

823
00:40:08,280 --> 00:40:09,940
someone starts slacking off.

824
00:40:10,630 --> 00:40:11,630
Has Song Yiting left?

825
00:40:11,630 --> 00:40:12,360
Relax.

826
00:40:12,360 --> 00:40:14,360
I watched her leave with my own eyes.

827
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:17,000
We're drowning in work,

828
00:40:17,000 --> 00:40:18,610
and you're sitting here drinking?

829
00:40:18,610 --> 00:40:20,000
I do brain work,

830
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:21,070
not grunt work.

831
00:40:21,070 --> 00:40:22,030
What did you do?

832
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:24,480
Helping Chief get rid of Song Yiting.

833
00:40:25,360 --> 00:40:26,330
Never mind.

834
00:40:26,630 --> 00:40:28,070
My amazing face

835
00:40:28,070 --> 00:40:29,150
and unmatched charm

836
00:40:29,150 --> 00:40:30,910
are heaven's gifts

837
00:40:31,110 --> 00:40:33,630
and my lifelong curse.

838
00:40:34,150 --> 00:40:35,030
Seriously?

839
00:40:35,230 --> 00:40:36,960
Miss Song Yiting likes Chief.

840
00:40:36,960 --> 00:40:38,000
He wears a mask.

841
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:39,330
It's not about his face.

842
00:40:40,070 --> 00:40:41,630
And it sure isn't about you.

843
00:40:49,960 --> 00:40:51,280
Qianyu Moon-Cleaving Blade is missing.

844
00:40:51,280 --> 00:40:52,080
It was stolen.

845
00:40:52,400 --> 00:40:53,360
Who's got the nerve

846
00:40:53,360 --> 00:40:54,710
to steal from Waning River Crescent?

847
00:40:54,710 --> 00:40:55,590
Yunlong, after them!

848
00:40:55,590 --> 00:40:56,230
No need.

849
00:40:58,490 --> 00:41:01,210
[Come to the garden of the Song
Residence at noon tomorrow. Yiting]

850
00:40:58,840 --> 00:40:59,840
Come to the garden

851
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:02,030
of the Song Residence at noon tomorrow.

